1940;;Laugh It Off;;British;;John Baxter;;Tommy Trinder, Jean Colin;;musical comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Laugh_It_Off_(1940_film);;At the start of World War II, Concert party entertainer Tommy Towers is drafted into service. He immediately gets on the wrong side of commanding officer Sergeant Major Slaughter, but after saving the camp show with his show business expertise, Tommy is granted a commission.